<p>There is struct:</p>  <pre><code>        [StructLayout(LayoutKind.Sequential)]         public struct WAVEFORMATEX         {             public ushort wFormatTag;             public ushort nChannels;             public ushort nSamplesPerSec;             public uint nAvgBytesPerSec;             public ushort nBlockAlign;             public ushort wBitsPerSample;             public ushort cbSize;         };         public WAVEFORMATEX audioInfo = new WAVEFORMATEX(); </code></pre>  <p>Why <strong>Marshal.SizeOf(audioInfo)</strong> returns 20 instead of 16?</p>